### Generate an image with Stable Diffusion (local GPU)
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{"input": "Generate an image of a sunset over mountains with golden light"}

### Generate with specific seed for reproducibility
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{"input": "Generate an image of a futuristic city at night with seed 42"}

### Generate with FLUX.2 (cloud, higher quality)
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{"input": "Use FLUX.2 to generate a photorealistic image of a coffee cup on a wooden table"}

### List available models
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{"input": "What image generation models are available?"}
